			<title>The First Dawn</title>
			<description>It&rsquo;s 5:30am. The first shades of light are appearing over the horizon. Like purple and orange waves, they pass through a clauster of milky clouds. They kindly snorkel on the waves of light, in the ocean of the sky. The songs of birds fly beyond the dark woods, now sailing and then descending.</description>
